article.description: — Keon Clergeot scored 17 points, Jalyn Hinton registered 13 points, seven rebounds and four blocks and Southeastern Louisiana narrowly beat Troy 72-68 on Sunday.
article.headline: Hinton scores 13 to lift SE Louisiana past Troy 72-68
article.linkText: Hinton scores 13 to lift SE Louisiana past Troy 72-68
article.story: TROY, Ala. -- — Keon Clergeot scored 17 points, Jalyn Hinton registered 13 points, seven rebounds and four blocks and Southeastern Louisiana narrowly beat Troy 72-68 on Sunday. Joe Kasperzyk added 14 points and Nick Caldwell had 11 points for Southeastern Louisiana (4-5). Efe Odigie had 18 points and 10 rebounds for the Trojans (5-4). Zay Williams added 12 points and Duke Miles had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
